Articles.Content:
**After reaching every planet in ksp with a 3 man-crew, AeroSpace has expanded to landing probes on those vast areas. For instance, the AeroSpace Tartu-X and Maverick-V, CC-75, Explorer 35, all in which are either in orbit or landed on these vast planets. Now AeroSpace is sending their first rover to Eve. Do they succeed? Do they fall in the molten sea and cry because they forgot to quicksave? Or does he just plain out quit? Find out below.** ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)
